  "text": "### Scenario 5: Account Restrictions  \n**Your Issue:** \"My account was frozen without explanation.\"  \n**What We Investigate:**\n- Why was it frozen? (Regulatory reason? Fraud hold? Other?)\n- Was proper notice given?\n- Was the freeze justified?  \n**Possible Outcomes:**\n- **Justified:** Explain reason (e.g., KYC compliance, fraud investigation); timeline for resolution\n- **Unjustified:** Unfreeze immediately; apologize; compensation\n- **Process error:** Unfreeze; improve process  \n**Typical Resolution Time:** 3–5 business days  \n---",
